feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 24, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zvh1665703197426.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zvh1665703197426.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zvh1665703197426.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zvh1665703197426\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">UROUTER_SET \n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Change settings for the Uniface Router.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__topic_d135434e1_d135435e1_d135436e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__p_d135437e1_d135438e1_d135439e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">operation UROUTER_SET</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">params</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"> numeric</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Maxclients</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (I2)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"> numeric</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Maxservers</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (I2)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"> numeric</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Maxmons</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (I2)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"> numeric</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IOPrint</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (I4)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"> string</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Message</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C80)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">endparams</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__section_vpp_vp1_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d877841e114\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__ul_pbz_vp1_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__li_d48047e1_d48048e1_d48049e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Maxclients</var>—maximum clients allowed </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__li_d48050e1_d48051e1_d48052e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Maxservers</var>—maximum servers allowed </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__li_d48053e1_d48054e1_d48055e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Maxmons</var>—maximum monitors allowed </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__li_d48056e1_d48057e1_d48058e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IOPrint</var>—<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$IOPRINT</span> for the Uniface Router </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__li_d48059e1_d48060e1_d48061e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Message</var>—message that is displayed in all running monitors and returned\n          to new clients or monitors that are refused connections. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__section_brh_xp1_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d877841e156\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__p_d134921e1_d134922e1_d134923e1\">If successful, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to 0.\n        Otherwise, see the \"Return Codes\" section in <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html\" title=\"UROUTMON is an internal component that enables you to write your own Uniface Router monitor to access and modify the Uniface Router's parameters and settings.\">UROUTMON</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__section_rph_gr1_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d877841e175\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__p_d135212e1_d135213e1_d135214e1\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__section_h2k_3r1_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d877841e184\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__p_d135458e1_d135459e1_d135460e1\">The privileged-user operation\n          <span class=\"keyword apiname\">UROUTER_SET</span> sets certain parameters for the Uniface Router dynamically.\n        You can limit or disallow the number of clients, servers, and monitors, and set the\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$IOPRINT</span> value for the Uniface Router.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zvh1665703197426__p_d135461e1_d135462e1_d135463e1\">For all maximum limits, the value -2 means no change,\n        and -1 means unlimited.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534639\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534639\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UROUTER_SET Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 24, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 UROUTER_SET Change settings for the Uniface Router. operation UROUTER_SET params numeric Maxclients : IN ; (I2) numeric Maxservers : IN ; (I2) numeric Maxmons : IN ; (I2) numeric IOPrint : IN ; (I4) string Message : IN ; (C80) endparams Parameters Maxclients —maximum clients allowed Maxservers —maximum servers allowed Maxmons —maximum monitors allowed IOPrint — $IOPRINT for the Uniface Router Message —message that is displayed in all running monitors and returned to new clients or monitors that are refused connections. Return Values If successful, $status is set to 0. Otherwise, see the \"Return Codes\" section in UROUTMON . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The privileged-user operation UROUTER_SET sets certain parameters for the Uniface Router dynamically. You can limit or disallow the number of clients, servers, and monitors, and set the $IOPRINT value for the Uniface Router. For all maximum limits, the value -2 means no change, and -1 means unlimited. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}